text: Willibrordus Pouw (8 January 1903 - 16 February 1986) was a Dutch gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1903 births Category:1986 deaths Category:Dutch male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the Netherlands Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Amsterdam
